140
00:14:44,779 --> 00:14:47,769
SPEAKER_27: I am very sorry, but you've got nothing left.

141
00:14:48,049 --> 00:14:51,779
SPEAKER_27: What could you stake the bet on?
We don't accept empty bets.

163
00:17:30,210 --> 00:17:32,400
SPEAKER_27: Mr. Xu, any mistakes?

289
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:45,220
SPEAKER_27: The wounded who froze to death.

313
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,460
SPEAKER_27: So, no running?

327
00:36:38,489 --> 00:36:39,719
SPEAKER_27: Fugui...

328
00:36:40,559 --> 00:36:42,889
SPEAKER_27: we've got to make it back alive.

697
01:20:36,289 --> 01:20:37,779
SPEAKER_27: District Chief, let's go.

699
01:20:43,329 --> 01:20:44,560
SPEAKER_27: Go away!

700
01:20:52,140 --> 01:20:53,439
SPEAKER_27: All right.

701
01:20:54,010 --> 01:20:55,340
SPEAKER_27: I'm going.

822
01:31:36,520 --> 01:31:38,449
SPEAKER_27: We must be going.

829
01:32:01,979 --> 01:32:04,810
SPEAKER_27: Thanks, we'll go to the factory bathhouse.

863
01:36:16,430 --> 01:36:17,989
SPEAKER_27: Chairman Mao...

864
01:36:18,869 --> 01:36:21,600
SPEAKER_27: Comrade Fengxia's mine now.

913
01:41:23,939 --> 01:41:28,000
SPEAKER_27: I just came from the hospital.
The doctor says it's due in autumn.

944
01:43:25,989 --> 01:43:28,829
SPEAKER_27: He's been arrested as a capitalist.

945
01:43:29,000 --> 01:43:31,829
SPEAKER_27: They held a public trial against him.

1043
01:50:54,909 --> 01:50:56,640
SPEAKER_27: Everything will be fine.

1075
01:53:19,020 --> 01:53:22,050
SPEAKER_27: This is the same Wang Bin
who once insulted...

1076
01:53:22,460 --> 01:53:26,359
SPEAKER_27: me and my wife,
saying she wasn't fit to reproduce.

1078
01:53:31,029 --> 01:53:33,159
SPEAKER_27: We dragged him here today...

1079
01:53:33,300 --> 01:53:36,270
SPEAKER_27: to educate him, to criticize him...

1080
01:53:37,340 --> 01:53:39,899
SPEAKER_27: and to let him witness her giving birth.

1086
01:54:03,300 --> 01:54:05,289
SPEAKER_27: That's professor Wang...

1087
01:54:05,500 --> 01:54:07,229
SPEAKER_27: head of obstetrics.

1088
01:54:15,010 --> 01:54:17,029
SPEAKER_27: Dr. Wang, don't be afraid.

1160
01:59:40,970 --> 01:59:43,159
SPEAKER_27: 7.9 pounds is excellent.

1161
01:59:43,239 --> 01:59:45,760
SPEAKER_27: If you get a car from the factory...

1162
01:59:45,840 --> 01:59:48,399
SPEAKER_27: we can drive Fengxia home.

1171
02:00:25,310 --> 02:00:28,539
SPEAKER_27: You two get the car, we'll be fine.

1172
02:00:40,989 --> 02:00:42,590
SPEAKER_27: Have some water.

1253
02:07:11,979 --> 02:07:13,350
SPEAKER_27: It's okay.

1262
02:07:42,550 --> 02:07:44,180
SPEAKER_27: Not just buns...

1263
02:07:44,279 --> 02:07:46,310
SPEAKER_27: anything made from wheat.

